embly and three students of the Ahmadu Bello University, Zaria. September 8, 2019 In "News" Kaduna State Police Command, said it had neutralised three and arrested 25 notorious suspected kidnappers in different operations in the state. September 8, 2019 In "News" THE Defence Head quarters, yesterday, said combined forces of 818 Battalion in conjunction with troops of Operation Sharan Daji, killed five bandits in Sabon Birni and Dangulbi villages in Sokoto State. May 11, 2019 In "News"